modules.description: This module generates sitemap files for a static site, providing functions to configure sitemap output paths, set update frequencies and priorities for document types, and collect URL entries with metadata. It works with document types, URL lists, and configuration maps to define per-type sitemap behaviors. Concrete use cases include building XML sitemaps with last-modified dates, setting default priorities for blog posts or pages, and integrating sitemap generation into site build pipelines.
